					<p><b>Note:</b> There are various levels of cookie enablement and disablement in Safari. For more information on cookie settings in Safari, see the following page: <br><a href="http://support.apple.com/kb/HT1677?viewlocale=en_US" target="_blank">http://support.apple.com/kb/HT1677?viewlocale=en_US</a></p>
